{"tid":1437334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"北角呢個地方真係唔抵幫","createTime":"2019-08-09T13:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T13:43:35.000Z","uid":14484,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"160ccfe6afebda727d8cce4db09230d4c4698573","tid":1437334,"uid":14484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"唔係想講有關星期日，係想講返今日喺北角有單企跳件事<br />\n有人企跳，你八掛望/影相我阻唔到你<br />\n但係你班廢中老街坊係咪咁撚冷血涼薄！？<br />\n事緣聽到有隻蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母！係跳就快撚啲跳啦，跳啦！跳啦！come on baby </span></strong></span>（係操純正廣東話）<br />\n<br />\n隔離粥舖又有個女人：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">死就快啲死啦阻住晒人，人地點行呀！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n後面又成堆廢老：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢喺度玩夠未/抵死啦/快啲啦</span></strong></span> 等等...<br />\n<br />\n路過真係聽到真係好心寒，一條人命嚟㗎仆街！<br />\n唔怪之得會有咁多人覺得爛塊玻璃仲緊要過六條人命<br />\n仲會覺得人命係咁低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有成條春秧街成條街都係啲大媽企街，係咪真係無枉管到咁！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ec362951b5d2a3b0674177dbf9ef95daec987d","tid":1437334,"uid":14484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:43:35.000Z","msg":"個蝻講完，成班人喺度笑嗰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係沒有一個是無辜的"}]}